# How to install ICEsceen locally?

The ICEscreen tool is a pipeline managed by snakemake.

1. Install conda

   See documentation: https://docs.conda.io/projects/conda/en/latest/user-guide/install/index.html

   Conda version must be **at least 4.10**

2. Install conda environments used by the ICEscreen pipeline:

   ./install_icescreen.sh
